          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>bbq sauce</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>bbq base</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1684910617244-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1684910617244-x400.jpg",
