            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>bbq base</strong> between the pizza bases and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p>",
