    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>pepper strips</strong>, <strong>sliced red onion</strong>, <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp – these are your <strong>bbq veggie loaded pizzas</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure the pizzas don’t overlap on the tray to avoid raw dough!</p>",
