    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pizzas are nearly done, wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to a large bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>, your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Toss it all together – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
